re with clear labeling of each object", "Effective synthesis that integrates the three analyses into an overarching conclusion"], "weaknesses": ["Absence of scholarly citations to support key claims", "Limited use of explicit TOK terminology and theoretical framing", "Occasional overly long sentences and minor structural clarity issues", "Lack of a dedicated introduction and separate conclusion section", "Insufficient critical engagement with counterarguments and cultural biases"], "calculationMethod": "Holistic AI evaluation: The strand assessment places this exhibition firmly in the 9\u00e2\u0080\u009310 band, noting its clear object identification, strong contextual grounding, explicit and sustained links to the IA prompt, and richly supported justifications. Minor stylistic and scholarly citation issues do not detract from the overall coherence, depth, and persuasiveness of the analysis. Given the work\u00e2\u0080\u0099s fulfillment of the highest\u00e2\u0080\u0090level descriptors across all aspects of the criterion, a maximum score of 10 is fully justified.", "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}], "strandSelections": [{"versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "strandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "selectedBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "bandScore": 10, "reasoning": "$49"}], "annotations": [{"id": "a0c18ac0-cf71-41d1-96f0-90a28a587106", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "width": 1, "height": 1}, "polygon": [{"x": 0, "y": 0}, {"x": 1, "y": 0}, {"x": 1, "y": 1}, {"x": 0, "y": 1}], "comment": "No scholarly references are provided up front. Consider citing key sources or frameworks early to anchor your analysis in established TOK scholarship.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "1821545e-690d-4723-9fab-e4fec4c714fa", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.125, "width": 0.3854, "height": 0.21500000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.5018, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.5018, "y": 0.34}, {"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.34}], "comment": "The image description is detailed; however, connecting visual features of the mirascope directly to the knowledge question (e.g. how illusion influences perception as a way of knowing) would deepen the TOK focus.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "5c04d246-1105-4ed2-bc3c-59b3de71395c", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.4347}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.7846}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.7846}], "comment": "The anecdote about your sister effectively conveys curiosity in action. To elevate this, analyze how this example illustrates specific ways of knowing (e.g. sense perception vs. reason).", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "58f71b70-c061-4c0c-ac62-4ab58ef92d50", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.5118}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8958}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8958}], "comment": "There is a strong link to personal motivation for seeking knowledge. To illustrate complexities, consider discussing debates about the DSM\u00e2\u0080\u0099s reliability and validity.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "96f25dc8-e7a0-4c67-8c42-6b97749ec0fc", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.2665, "y": 0.3475, "width": 0.4614, "height": 0.12130000000000002}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.2665, "y": 0.3475}, {"x": 0.7279, "y": 0.3475}, {"x": 0.7279, "y": 0.4688}, {"x": 0.2665, "y": 0.4688}], "comment": "The prompt is clearly stated, focusing the exhibition on \u00e2\u0080\u009cWhy do we seek knowledge?\u00e2\u0080\u009d. Consider integrating explicit TOK terminology (e.g. ways of knowing, knowledge frameworks) in the introduction to strengthen theoretical framing.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "3061a8f8-9d95-47bc-8f94-5b7dcd0baad9", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.46119999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.8078}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.8078}], "comment": "The Rorschach comparison is insightful. Include a brief critical discussion on whether projecting meaning onto random stimuli constitutes valid knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d382a4e6-cfe0-496c-ae6c-aa34c7aa6427", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.46119999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.8078}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.8078}], "comment": "The description of ever-changing patterns is vivid and demonstrates an appreciation for subjective interpretation in knowledge formation.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "88928b93-1583-4ecf-8064-58cde52217d7", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.5118}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8958}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8958}], "comment": "To deepen TOK engagement, critically assess how the DSM\u00e2\u0080\u0099s categorizations reflect cultural biases and influence what is accepted as knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "19b83e02-79d9-4b14-b4d3-b2a943753a1b", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 1, "bbox": {"x": 0.413, "y": 0.5076, "width": 0.1679, "height": 0.021299999999999986}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.413, "y": 0.5076}, {"x": 0.5809, "y": 0.5076}, {"x": 0.5809, "y": 0.5289}, {"x": 0.413, "y": 0.5289}], "comment": "While the word count is within range, the student should ensure that every sentence contributes to TOK analysis, avoiding repetition to enhance conciseness and depth.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "3d7f7f2a-a113-4743-8084-e8cb429b4ee0", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNum