d": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.4347}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.7846}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.7846}], "comment": "No scholarly citations accompany the discussion of optical illusion. Including a reference to a scientific source on perception would substantiate your analysis.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "d5dafaa8-d3d2-42ed-aa8f-ef9acd2cc8db", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0938, "width": 0.19920000000000002, "height": 0.0179}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0938}, {"x": 0.3119, "y": 0.0938}, {"x": 0.3119, "y": 0.1117}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1117}], "comment": "Clearly identifying \u00e2\u0080\u009cObject 2: Kaleidoscope\u00e2\u0080\u009d maintains a coherent structure across all objects.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "32d68111-03a0-4739-a43f-f2e97839b362", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.125, "width": 0.2745, "height": 0.2116}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.3909, "y": 0.125}, {"x": 0.3909, "y": 0.3366}, {"x": 0.1164, "y": 0.3366}], "comment": "The kaleidoscope image sets context. You could reference how rotating the tube parallels shifting perspectives in knowledge acquisition.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "88b28192-c731-4123-9cdc-d68684c01272", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.4347}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.7846}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.7846}], "comment": "This paragraph contains multiple run-on sentences. Consider dividing complex ideas into shorter sentences to improve clarity and readability.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "771bea36-7d3a-4a1e-bdbf-b7e88640a799", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 2, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.4347}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3499}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.7846}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.7846}], "comment": "The justification concludes with a broad statement about seeking knowledge. To provide depth, consider referencing TOK concepts like epistemic motivation or discuss a counterexample where curiosity might be discouraged.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "fb9f2495-d54d-4a95-a3c1-30eb27c79a07", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.5118}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8958}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8958}], "comment": "The final synthesis is embedded within object 3. Separating the conclusion into its own section would improve structural clarity and emphasize overarching insights.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "50c6076a-8e43-405a-a7dc-0c2bf29156b4", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.46119999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.8078}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.8078}], "comment": "Consider adding academic references on projective tests to avoid presenting assertions about the Rorschach test without evidence.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "cdbccf79-fa75-4d3b-9b1c-65d344c1c2ed", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 3, "bbox": {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466, "width": 0.7843, "height": 0.46119999999999994}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.3466}, {"x": 0.8958, "y": 0.8078}, {"x": 0.1115, "y": 0.8078}], "comment": "Some sentences are overly complex. Break them into shorter units and consider using LaTeX to represent geometrical relations if relevant.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "f2864293-f3c0-465e-99df-2a8025f177de", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0938, "width": 0.747, "height": 0.0189}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.0938}, {"x": 0.8597, "y": 0.0938}, {"x": 0.8597, "y": 0.1127}, {"x": 0.1127, "y": 0.1127}], "comment": "The title naming the DSM-5 is precise and informative, clearly situating the object within a knowledge context.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "0e87ebc2-ef74-47b8-8896-c8ed1b919758", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1158, "y": 0.1278, "width": 0.21809999999999996, "height": 0.2448}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1158, "y": 0.1278}, {"x": 0.3339, "y": 0.1278}, {"x": 0.3339, "y": 0.3726}, {"x": 0.1158, "y": 0.3726}], "comment": "The cover image supports context. Consider commenting on how its formal presentation reflects the institutional authority behind psychiatric knowledge.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "22e3eeb6-05c8-4d76-b7eb-737f6eed1cbd", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "strength", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.5118}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8958}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8958}], "comment": "The personal narrative linking the DSM to your own and your friend\u00e2\u0080\u0099s experience is compelling and grounded in authentic context.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}, {"id": "748d8da5-206d-48ec-be6d-c3605d62aa2b", "versionId": "02e628e8-612f-46dc-be38-a532669e2db5", "criterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "strandId": null, "type": "weakness", "pageNumber": 4, "bbox": {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384, "width": 0.7868, "height": 0.5118}, "polygon": [{"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.384}, {"x": 0.8977, "y": 0.8958}, {"x": 0.1109, "y": 0.8958}], "comment": "No scholarly citations accompany the discussion of the DSM-5. Including references to psychiatric literature would further substantiate your analysis of its epistemic role.", "color": null, "status": "unread", "statusUpdatedAt": null, "statusUpdatedBy": null, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition"}]}]}}, "rubricData": {"id": 57, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "version": 1, "status": "published", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:43.512632+00", "totalMarks": 10, "description": null, "type": "TOK", "rubricSpecificInfo": null, "tags": [""], "isArchived": false, "gradeBoundaryId": "52ad2701-27bc-42f3-be3f-d63b98d98139", "name": "TOK Exhibition", "slug": "tok-exhibition", "rubricCriteria": [{"id": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "revisionId": 57, "groupName": "TOK Exhibition", "label": null, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:55.358727+00", "updatedAt": "2025-07-16 11:21:18.828885+00", "isGradable": true, "showGradedScore": true, "isChecklistCriterion": false, "description": null, "rubricCriterionBands": [{"id": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 0, "marksTo": 0, "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:46.486581+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f7cb0652-0737-403e-8f65-be13bd2fd7f1", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "9ff6a42c-458d-4ba2-aed7-d0ce052fc68b", "content": "The exhibition does not reach the standard described by the other levels or does not use one of the IA prompts provided.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:58.577216+00"}]}, {"id": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 1, "marksTo": 2, "orderIndex": 1, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:47.076074+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "861f06ce-2b51-46ce-a6ee-3022e7080288", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "a1ba39dd-f4e1-46d0-92fb-f804616659df", "content": "The exhibition presents\nthree objects, but the\nreal-world contexts of\nthese objects are not\nstated, or the images\npresented may be\nhighly generic images of\ntypes of object rather\nthan of specific\nreal-world objects. Links\nbetween the objects\nand the selected IA\nprompt are made, but\nthese are minimal,\ntenuous, or it is not\nclear what the student is\ntrying to convey.\nThere is very little\njustification offered for\nthe inclusion of each\nobject in the exhibition.\nThe commentary on the\nobjects is highly\ndescriptive or consists\nonly of unsupported\nassertions.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:04.443183+00"}]}, {"id": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 3, "marksTo": 4, "orderIndex": 2, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.072006+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "e8acd337-a77d-4319-a744-06094151d57b", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "d33f3613-07e3-4130-984c-f84b6431e3e4", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of the objects may be implied rather than explicitly stated. Basic links between the objects and the selected IA prompt are made, but the explanation of these links is unconvincing and/or unfocused. There is a superficial justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Reasons for the inclusion of the objects are offered, but these are not supported by appropriate evidence and/or lack relevance to the selected IA prompt. There may be significant repetition across the justifications of the different objects", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:20.428881+00"}]}, {"id": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 5, "marksTo": 6, "orderIndex": 3, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:48.868343+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "c257e18a-e3b8-46f4-b3b9-d9ea5cd5db84", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "bd39c308-b52c-4662-b0f5-64d285be9e95", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects, although the real-world contexts of these objects may be vaguely or imprecisely stated. There is some explanation of the links between the three objects and the selected IA prompt. There is some justification for the inclusion of each object in the exhibition. Some of the points are supported by evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:31.312862+00"}]}, {"id": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 7, "marksTo": 8, "orderIndex": 4, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:49.555746+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "f16fe76e-abd8-4dc1-9a4f-50ab9e121c99", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "48708361-8824-4c01-bcbd-39c3e493de8e", "content": "The exhibition identifies three objects and their real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are explained, although this explanation may lack precision and clarity in parts. There is a justification of the contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. Many of the points are supported by appropriate evidence and references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:40.123527+00"}]}, {"id": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "marksFrom": 9, "marksTo": 10, "orderIndex": 5, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:04:50.346899+00", "rubricCriterionStrandBandContents": [{"id": "055fe2ad-3ef1-4074-af44-83cc3440cc7a", "rubricCriterionStrandId": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionBandId": "5552e9fd-0d0a-4bb2-9ece-5e7a3c438771", "content": "The exhibition clearly identifies three objects and their specific real-world contexts. Links between each of the three objects and the selected IA prompt are clearly made and well-explained. There is a strong justification of the particular contribution that each individual object makes to the exhibition. All, or nearly all, of the points are well-supported by appropriate evidence and explicit references to the selected IA prompt.", "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:05:51.46084+00"}]}], "rubricCriterionStrands": [{"id": "17a30166-bc52-427b-904b-44efbdd5c7d7", "rubricCriterionId": "cc70033e-f75e-42d2-8670-9501aa0d86a1", "orderIndex": 0, "createdAt": "2025-02-20 06:03:59.452498+00", "name": "Does the exhibition successfully show how TOK manifests in the world around us?"}]}]}, "similarExemplars": [{"id": "d1111437-1987-4ff1-b872-66c01db93cdd", "title": "Why do we seek knowledge?", "description": "", "tags": ["grade-C", "tok", "sl"], "slug": "why-do-we-seek-knowledge-2", "isPublic": true, "isPremium": true, "showScores": true, "createdAt": "2025-08-05T08:00:25.428Z", "userSubmissionId": "c29595f7-c016-4513-b728-531f86a45ea8", "submissionId": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a", "similarity": 0.542182776, "normalizedScore": 0.5, "compositeScore": 0.5295279432, "matchingFileId": "", "matchingChunkId": "", "matchingChunkNumber": 0, "userSubmission": {"id": "c29595f7-c016-4513-b728-531f86a45ea8", "score": "C", "scoreType": "letter", "level": null, "researchQuestion": null, "tokPrompt": null, "title": "Why do we seek knowledge?", "cohort": "M25", "createdAt": "2025-07-15T17:00:22.531Z", "subjectId": 582, "rubricId": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "subject": {"id": 582, "title": "Theory of Knowledge (TOK)", "slug": "ib-theory-of-knowledge-tok"}, "rubric": {"id": "15a001d0-4b6b-41b6-abae-4e9498385eaf", "title": "TOK Exhibition", "type": "TOK"}, "totalRawMark": 6, "totalModeratedMark": 5}, "submission": {"id": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a", "type": "TOK", "level": "SL", "createdAt": "2025-08-05T07:58:14.776Z", "files": [{"submissionId": "55a2123f-3165-4274-9df1-9c87b63a1d1a"